section: The exclusive purpose of the Venture (the "Purpose") will be IT Development. internet Back office Maintenance And Deployment of medical Service. This purpose may be changed at any time at the discretion of BorrowMoney.com, inc.
explanation: The contract states that the venture's exclusive purpose will be IT development, internet back office maintenance and deployment of medical service. However, it also states that the purpose may be changed at any time at the discretion of BorrowMoney.com, inc. This contradicts the "exclusive" nature of the stated purpose, as it can be unilaterally altered.

section: Any vote required by the Members will be determined such that each Member receives one vote, however, BorrowMoney.com, inc.'s vote will carry twice the weight of JVLS, LLC dba Vaccines 2Go's vote.
explanation: The contract outlines that each member receives one vote; however, BorrowMoney.com, Inc.'s vote will carry twice the weight of JVLS, LLC dba Vaccines 2Go's vote. In essence, BorrowMoney.com, Inc. has a larger say than JVLS, LLC.

section: This Agreement may be amended with the consent of BorrowMoney.com, inc., notwithstanding any objection from JVLS, LLC dba Vaccines 2Go.
explanation: The contract states that the agreement may be amended with the consent of BorrowMoney.com, inc, notwithstanding any objection from JVLS, LLC dba Vaccines 2Go. In essence, BorrowMoney.com, Inc. has the authority to change and amend the agreement without the concent of JVLS, LLC.
